membrance-al-dhikr","tag-reward-al-ajr","tag-strength-al-quwwah","tag-trees","tag-water-al-maa"],"aioseo_notices":[],"jetpack_featured_media_url":"","jetpack_shortlink":"https:\/\/wp.me\/p95VHY-93h","jetpack_sharing_enabled":true,"jetpack-related-posts":[{"id":20983,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/04\/dhikr-halaqah-riyad-al-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34799,"position":0},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: Circles of remembrance are gardens of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Anas ibn Malik reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you pass by the meadows of Paradise, graze as you like.\u201d They said, \u201cWhat are the meadows of Paradise?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cCircles of remembrance.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3510 Grade: Hasan (fair) according to\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Righteousness \u0627\u0644\u0628\u0631","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/righteousness-al-birr\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20985,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/10\/04\/masjid-riyad-al-jannah-dhikr\/","url_meta":{"origin":34799,"position":1},"title":"Hadith on Masajid: Mosques of Allah are gardens of Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"October 4, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Abu Huraira reported: The Messenger of Allah, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhen you pass by the meadows of Paradise, graze as you like.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the meadows of Paradise?\u201d The Prophet said, \u201cThe mosques.\u201d I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":20188,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2015\/01\/20\/dua-hamd-trees-paradise\/","url_meta":{"origin":34799,"position":2},"title":"Hadith on Dua: Trees planted in Paradise when praising Allah","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"January 20, 2015","format":false,"excerpt":"Jabir reported: The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cWhoever declares the glory of Allah and his praise will have a palm tree planted for him in Paradise.\u201d Source: Sunan al-Tirmidhi\u0304 3464 Grade: Sahih (authentic) according to Al-Albani \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u062c\u064e\u0627\u0628\u0650\u0631\u064d \u0639\u064e\u0646\u0652 \u0627\u0644\u0646\u0651\u064e\u0628\u0650\u064a\u0651\u0650 \u0635\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0649 \u0627\u0644\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0647\u064f \u0639\u064e\u0644\u064e\u064a\u0652\u0647\u0650 \u0648\u064e\u0633\u064e\u0644\u0651\u064e\u0645\u064e \u0642\u064e\u0627\u0644\u064e \u0645\u064e\u0646\u0652\u2026","rel":"","context":"In &quot;Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646&quot;","block_context":{"text":"Faith \u0627\u0644\u0627\u064a\u0645\u0627\u0646","link":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/category\/faith-iman\/"},"img":{"alt_text":"","src":"","width":0,"height":0},"classes":[]},{"id":34764,"url":"https:\/\/www.abuaminaelias.com\/dailyhadithonline\/2020\/12\/23\/spoils-dhikr-jannah\/","url_meta":{"origin":34799,"position":3},"title":"Hadith on Dhikr: The spoils of remembrance is Paradise","author":"Abu Amina Elias","date":"December 23, 2020","format":false,"excerpt":"Abdullah ibn Amr reported: I said, \u201cO Messenger of Allah, what are the spoils of gathering to remember Allah?\u201d The Prophet, peace and blessings be upon him, said, \u201cThe spoils of the gatherings of remembrance is Paradise.\u201d Source: Musnad Ah\u0323